block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: This origami drone boomerang is designed by one of my friend channels @Origami & Crafts . Throw this drone with a spin and an angle and it will fly back to you. It's quite fun! This is a quick version go to @Origami & Crafts for a slow version of the video. I hope you enjoy it! Checkout the original video here : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OvyJmw3Ux70 Thanks For Watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
